課程概述 Course Description
       本課程討論在R^n上的Lebesgue測度和實函數Lebesgue積分理論。The Theory of Lebesgue on R^n, Lebesgue Integration on R^n.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    This course in the Autumn semester is designed to give a standard introduction at the beginning graduate level to measure theory and the theory of the Lebesgue integral. Students will learn the basic techniques and theorems of analysis.    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Preliminaries2Preliminaries3Functions of Bounded Variations4Functions of Bounded Variations5Lebesgue Measure and Outer Measure6Lebesgue Measure and Outer Measure7Lebesgue Measure and Outer Measure8Lebesgue Measurable Functions9Lebesgue Measurable Functions10The Lebesgue Integral11The Lebesgue Integral12The Lebesgue Integral13The Lebesgue Integral14Repeated Integration 15Repeated Integration 16Repeated Integration17The Classical Banach Spaces18The Classical Banach Spaces 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


