�ҵ{�W���ƭȤ��R(�@)Numerical Analysis I
�ҵ{²�����ҵ{�[�\�ƭȤ��R���D�n�����A�]�A�G��ƨt�P�B�I�ƨt�ΡA��T�סA�ǽT�שM�~�t���R�A�������D�ڤ�k�M���ĩʤ��R�A�u�ʨt�μƭȤ�k�A�ƭȷL����{�A�H�ά�����í�w�ʤ��R�P�ƭȤ�k�CThis course covers main concepts of numerical analysis, including: real number system v.s. floating number system, precision, accuarcy and error analysis, higher dimensional root finding methods and convergence analysis, numerical methods for linear systems, numerical differential equations, and related stability analysis. 





�ҵ{�W���ֳt�p���kFast Computational Method
